# Nuvora Agency — Netlify Redirects
# https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects/

# Force HTTPS
http://nuvora-agency.netlify.app/* https://nuvora-agency.netlify.app/:splat 301!
http://nuvora.agency/* https://nuvora.agency/:splat 301!

# www to non-www redirect (once custom domain added)
https://www.nuvora.agency/* https://nuvora.agency/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback — serve index.html for all routes
/*    /index.html   200
